name: int_add_four_way_regrouping
section: arithmetic
args: a:Int b:Int c:Int d:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Addition of four generated values must be stable under regrouping and re-pairing.
law: (= (fuzz-add (fuzz-add {a} {b}) (fuzz-add {c} {d})) (fuzz-add (fuzz-add {a} {c}) (fuzz-add {b} {d})))
